author: PostmodernJukebox
description:
“Gimme! Gimme! Gimme! (A Man After Midnight)” by ABBA Peggy Lee style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Lauren De Marco.
Get The Song on our new album: http://pmjlive.com/llm || World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com
 Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ || PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

Here's a PMJ debut from our new album: Jazz chanteuse Lauren De Marco brings her " film noir" vocal tone and exquisite phrasing to this Peggy Lee-style remake of ABBA's 1979 hit, "Gimme! Gimme! Gimme! (A Man After Midnight)."
